{"vocabInfos":[{"lsjDefs":"<b> ἐπιρρίπτ-ω</b> <br /> (ἐπῐρίπτω [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" “Anthologia Graeca” 5.128 (1st c.AD: Automedon Epigrammaticus))\">Refs 1st c.AD+</a>], <b>cast at</b>, ὅτε μοι χαλκήρεα δοῦρα Τρῶες ἐπέρριψαν [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 8th c.BC: Odyssea Homerus Epicus “Odyssey” 5.310 \">Refs 8th c.BC+</a>]; διώκων ἐ. ἑαυτόν <b>throws</b> himself <b>upon</b> his prey, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 4th c.BC: Aristoteles Philosophus “Historia Animalium” 629b20 \">Refs 4th c.BC+</a>]; Βρούτῳ τὴν αὑτοῦ φοινικίδα ἐ. [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 1st-2nd c.AD: Plutarchus Biographus et Philosophus “Antonius” 22 \">Refs 1st c.AD+</a>]; χεῖρα ἐ., Latin <i>manum injecit,</i> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" Anthologia Graeca 9.84 (1st c.AD: Antiphanes Macedo Epigrammaticus): _metaphorically_, ἐ. πλάνας τινί 4th-5th c.BC: Aeschylus Tragicus “Prometheus Vinctus” 738 \">Refs 4th c.BC+</a>]; ψευδεῖς αἰτίας ἐ. [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 1st c.BC: Diodorus Siculus Historicus 14.12 \">Refs 1st c.BC+</a>]; τὴν μέριμναν ἐπὶ [θεόν] [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" NT.1Pet.5.7 \">NT</a>]; <b>inflict</b>, πολλὰσκληρὰ.. ἐπιρριφήσεται, with <i>dative</i>, Nech.in [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" “Catalogus Codicum Astrologorum” 7.146. \">Refs</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__2</b></Level3>. <b>apply</b> a plaster or fomentation, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 2nd c.AD: Soranus Medicus 1.50 (_passive_), 69; σκεπάσματα 1st c.AD: Dioscorides (Dioscurides) Medicus 5.88. \">Refs 1st c.AD+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__3</b></Level3>. <i>passive</i>, -όμενα σκιρρώματα <b>spreading over the surface</b>, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] 1.42. \">Refs</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__4</b></Level3>. <b>requisition</b>, ἔργα [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" “PTeb.” 5.249 (2nd c.BC); ἱερεῖα τρέφειν [prev. work] 183. \">Refs 2nd c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__5</b></Level3>. <i>metaphorically</i> in <i>passive</i>, <b>to be imminent</b>, οὐ βραχὺς ἐπέρριπτο κίνδυνος [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 1st c.AD: Philo Judaeus 2.594. \">Refs 1st c.AD+</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__II</b></Level2>. <b>throw out opinions</b>, ἀδιορίστως ἐ. περὶ τῶν λοιπῶν, variant for -, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 4th c.BC: Aristoteles Philosophus “Metaphysica” 986a34. \">Refs 4th c.BC+</a>]","strongNumber":"G1977","accentedUnicode":"ἐπιρρίπτω","relatedNos":[{"strongNumber":"G0306","matchingForm":"ἀναβάλλω","stepTransliteration":"anaballō","gloss":"to defer","_zh_tw_Gloss":"拖延","_es_Gloss":"aplazar","_zh_Gloss":"拖延"},{"strongNumber":"G0474","matchingForm":"ἀντιβάλλω","stepTransliteration":"antiballō","gloss":"to discuss","_zh_tw_Gloss":"談論","_es_Gloss":"conversar","_zh_Gloss":"谈论"},{"strongNumber":"G0577","matchingForm":"ἀποβάλλω","stepTransliteration":"apoballō","gloss":"to throw away","_zh_tw_Gloss":"丟下","_es_Gloss":"desechar, arrojar","_zh_Gloss":"丢下"},{"strongNumber":"G0641","matchingForm":"ἀπορρίπτω","stepTransliteration":"aporriptō","gloss":"to throw off","_zh_tw_Gloss":"跳下","_es_Gloss":"echar","_zh_Gloss":"跳下"},{"strongNumber":"G0906G","matchingForm":"βάλλω","stepTransliteration":"ballō","gloss":"to throw: throw","_zh_tw_Gloss":"丟","_es_Gloss":"echar","_zh_Gloss":"丢"},{"strongNumber":"G0906H","matchingForm":"βάλλω","stepTransliteration":"ballō","gloss":"to throw: put","_zh_tw_Gloss":"丟","_es_Gloss":"echar","_zh_Gloss":"丢"},{"strongNumber":"G0906I","matchingForm":"βάλλω","stepTransliteration":"ballō","gloss":"to throw: sow","_zh_tw_Gloss":"丟","_es_Gloss":"echar","_zh_Gloss":"丢"},{"strongNumber":"G0906J","matchingForm":"βάλλω","stepTransliteration":"ballō","gloss":"to throw: pour","_zh_tw_Gloss":"丟","_es_Gloss":"echar","_zh_Gloss":"丢"},{"strongNumber":"G1225","matchingForm":"διαβάλλω","stepTransliteration":"diaballō","gloss":"to accuse","_zh_tw_Gloss":"被告到","_es_Gloss":"acusar ","_zh_Gloss":"被告到"},{"strongNumber":"G1544","matchingForm":"ἐκβάλλω",